The paper deals with collaborative security initiatives and predictive blacklisting, which are topics related to computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves measurement analysis and machine learning techniques to improve the effectiveness of the system (cs.LG). The privacy-preserving aspect of the proposed approach suggests that it may also fall under the sub-category of secure information exchange (cs.SI). The scalability aspect of the proposed approach may also relate to distributed systems (cs.DS) and distributed computing (cs.DC).
